It seems a little weird to be refactoring this interface (which is itself quite weird) when we have the re-write pending. I get that the point is to have this converted in case the rewrite patch doesn't land or is blocked in some way. However, I wonder if it's really worth doing this, or holding this until after FF and only merging it (as is) if the other one fails to land and we punt?
